{"tid":1968914,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想唔想連非洲都boycott中國？","createTime":"2020-04-12T05:17:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T05:32:08.000Z","uid":350216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e869783aeb4c3c338334fbcc60762e2d39ff4b54","tid":1968914,"uid":350216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T05:17:10.000Z","msg":"事源廣州大規模驅趕黑人，好多人流離失所，仲想屈佢地播毒，支那網絡上鬧得好難聽，已經引起好多黑人不滿，肯尼亞外交部同中國外交部已經進行交涉。<br />\n<br />\nBoycott支那，人人有責<br />\n雖然非洲國際影響力唔大，但係唔好放過任何一個鞭屍中國既機會，與其俾中國爭取到做盟友，不如令佢地關係破裂。<br />\n唔好唔記得譚生菜上到位，同爭取到非洲50國支持有關。<br />\n<br />\n上Twitter撥火<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429bab7c111d3a335267e731ed5ccf43c339be34","tid":1968914,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T05:20:19.000Z","msg":"非洲咁多一帶一路<br />\n點會冇影響呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b979f1312b9d4fe85f9b03ba661b465f4c98e3f","tid":1968914,"uid":350216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T05:20:24.000Z","msg":"#chinamustexplain"},{"pid":"888f95945d628b1461266137064158862d0b9ac6","tid":1968914,"uid":350216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T05:20:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gbTd8VL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgbTd8VL.jpg&h=092f577f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/12/131937_6c73f0fec37a60545af53f614a4b4a50.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F12%2F131937_6c73f0fec37a60545af53f614a4b4a50.png&h=816b0e08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"784ad75f54d0b37c9403b9b9ce732970c5412e71","tid":1968914,"uid":350216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T05:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/12/132055_57841939699a971337b85715137e18a2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://